pod is an instance of the application deploy on the kubernet cluster - application can have one container or more

deploymet is mutiple set of pods, single induval pod or set of pods. mutiiple instance of pods deployment of cluster

services is logical set of pods.


kube Master node - will handle all the deployment of the worker node. 
                   If you have mutiple nodes in the kubernet cluster, which port has to goes to which node.

Kube Worker node - Creates the port and Creates the container runtime(most of the container runtime is docker )

Master node - will do all the admistration tasks of the kubernet cluster.
Worker node - were the actual application or container , were ports are created and maintained.
